{"source_url": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/ChNXTUuJQiQ/", "scraped_at": "2026-06-26T23:10:26.195072+00:00", "id": "2904079817712666768", "description": "“I know my nails are going to turn a little yellow after this — but the food is good.” ❤️💛 \n \nMeet @maitreyiramakrishnan (Maitreyi Ramakrishnan), star of the @netflix series “Never Have I Ever.” To celebrate the premiere of season three, which explores experiences surrounding the South Asian diaspora, Maitreyi spent a day in NYC on an epic food tour. \n \n“This is a very heartwarming moment for me because everyone is appreciating food that I’ve grown up with my entire life,” says Maitreyi as she samples a dosa from a busy food cart. “This is Tamil pride right here. This makes me so happy. It’s not just people in the film industry, it’s all different industries in all different ways, and that to me is cultural appreciation — because that line is really diverse.” \n \nFollow Maitreyi as she tastes foods (and some very spicy spices 😂) from Sri Lanka, Nepal and Malaysia. 🔥❤️✨ \n \nMusic by @tesherrrr", "created_at": 1660413382, "author": {"id": "25025320", "unique_id": "instagram", "nickname": null, "verified": null, "signature": null, "followers": null, "following": null, "likes": null, "videos": null}, "stats": {"plays": 13446730, "likes": 784091, "comments": 9394, "shares": null, "saves": null}, "video": {"duration": 132, "ratio": null, "cover": "https://scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/639969689_1487215666072741_7648687321824705402_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_p1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEVmHLbNoL_qPUDNLWOlyKdObD13Wkevbgfbjx_fd5d-9TX8fZ6Muo44cUmMzuczoo&_nc_ohc=B5FWz71Da28Q7kNvwGl07qy&_nc_gid=rdQLjriBxfX9gxPYXB0m3w&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_p0nJqOVNKKC2JWuYih2TY7rv7kIAqMY7c2oGfCy55bQ&oe=6A44D08D&_nc_sid=8b3546", "dynamic_cover": null, "origin_cover": null, "play_url": "https://scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQNGIV1PwvMKJc8m