{"source_url": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cb5WT-Uhj6Z/", "scraped_at": "2026-06-26T23:10:26.196187+00:00", "id": "2808373972251852441", "description": "Artist Jon Batiste (@jonbatiste) is a whole vibe. 🎶 He’s heading to the Grammy Awards (@recordingacademy) with 11 different nominations — the most of any nominee this year. 🤯👏\n\nBut before Jon’s performance at the awards, he met up with friends in New York City for one of his self-proclaimed “love riots.”\n\n“Love riots are like chaotic, fun, impromptu musical parades. It started as something I would do in transit from one place to the next, whether on the way to the recording studio or to rehearsal or even just to the market,” says Jon. “It borrows from the second-line tradition of my hometown New Orleans, typically starting with a few people and gathering folks along the way. I love the feeling of ceremony and sense of community that it brings.”\n\nMeet Jon’s community and hear his soulful sound from the subway to the studio before tonight’s show in Las Vegas.", "created_at": 1649004405, "author": {"id": "25025320", "unique_id": "instagram", "nickname": null, "verified": null, "signature": null, "followers": null, "following": null, "likes": null, "videos": null}, "stats": {"plays": 6231377, "likes": 370844, "comments": 9125, "shares": null, "saves": null}, "video": {"duration": 121, "ratio": null, "cover": "https://scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/639810216_4487386284841586_6413889215035305812_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gEVmHLbNoL_qPUDNLWOlyKdObD13Wkevbgfbjx_fd5d-9TX8fZ6Muo44cUmMzuczoo&_nc_ohc=VLKs_VRS2sQQ7kNvwGuNz55&_nc_gid=rdQLjriBxfX9gxPYXB0m3w&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af8D8n4Jm8jKeyxzvnRu8TOK4bm6hru-ZWkkv-TwVfhu6Q&oe=6A44C3DB&_nc_sid=8b3546", "dynamic_cover": null, "origin_cover": null, "play_url": "https://scontent-iev1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQMkgrelzoL7JeLUp5xSIYgriBbT0eVPJdEPw8vDQmNmdpGcL